E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_game` values('2359','21','0','','','','1','admin','|37|63|','1','0','1343228627','0','0','0','0','','','2359','0','0','0','0','0','0','铸成大错','1343228627','/spic/20120725/5080.jpg','0','1','1343228627','0','3','1','0','','0','','/d/file/swf/098.swf','667','479','','1','','0','','1','/dpic/20120725/5081.jpg','7942','VEhwTmRVMURPSGRPYVRoM1QxUm5kV016WkcwPQ==','0','0','http://s.61baobao.com/3.0/06/098.swf','http://www.61baobao.com/3.0/06/dpic/098.jpg','http://www.61baobao.com/3.0/06/pic/098.jpg','0','三个月以上','0','','0','','0','0','0');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_game` values('2360','21','0','','','','1','admin','|37|63|','1','0','1343228627','0','0','0','0','','','2360','0','0','0','0','0','0','经典成语_纸上谈兵','1343228627','/spic/20120725/5120.jpg','0','1','1343228627','0','3','1','0','','0','','/d/file/swf/088.swf','667','479','战国时赵国名将赵奢之子赵括，年轻时学兵法，谈起兵事来父亲也难不倒他。后来他接替廉颇为赵将，在长平之战中，只知道根据兵书办，不知道变通，贸然进攻，结果被秦军打败。<br /><br />释义：比喻空谈理论而没有实际经验，不能解决实际问题。也比喻空谈不能成为现实。 ','1','','0','','1','/dpic/20120725/5121.jpg','7932','VEhwTmRVMURPSGRPYVRoM1QwUm5kV016WkcwPQ==','0','0','http://s.61baobao.com/3.0/06/088.swf','http://www.61baobao.com/3.0/06/dpic/088.jpg','http://www.61baobao.com/3.0/06/pic/088.jpg','0','三个月以上','0','','0','','0','0','0');");
