E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_game` values('2480','18','0','','','','1','admin','','1','0','1343229737','0','0','0','0','','','2480','0','0','0','0','0','0','小红帽 2','1343229737','/spic/20120725/2874.jpg','0','1','1343229737','0','3','1','0','','0','','/d/file/swf/088.swf','667','479','从前有个可爱的小姑娘，谁见了都喜欢，但最喜欢她的是她的奶奶，简直是她要什么就给她什么。一次，奶奶送给小姑娘一顶用丝绒做的小红帽，戴在她的头上正好合适。从此，姑娘再也不愿意戴任何别的帽子，于是大家便叫她“小红帽”。','1','','0','','1','/dpic/20120725/2875.jpg','11018','VERKT2RtSlhNWFppYVRsdFlrZEdlbUZET0hsTlJFVjRXV2s0ZDA5RE9IZFBSR2QxWXpOa2JRPT0=','0','0','http://s.61baobao.com/common/flash/2011b/08/088.swf','http://www.61baobao.com/common/flash/2011b/08/dpic/088.jpg','http://www.61baobao.com/common/flash/2011b/08/pic/088.jpg','0','三个月以上','0','','0','','0','0','0');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_game` values('2481','18','0','','','','1','admin','','1','0','1343229738','0','0','0','0','','','2481','0','0','0','0','0','0','小熊生病','1343229738','/spic/20120725/2846.jpg','0','1','1343229738','0','3','1','0','','0','','/d/file/swf/098.swf','667','479','灰狗、黄羊、花鹿是小熊最好的朋友，一次，小熊生了重病，朋友们都来家里看望。灰狗一进门，就大声啷啷，：”“哎呀，我的兄弟，听说你生病了，真叫人着急啊！瞧你，脸色这么差。“','1','','0','','1','/dpic/20120725/2847.jpg','11028','VERKT2RtSlhNWFppYVRsdFlrZEdlbUZET0hsTlJFVjRXV2s0ZDA5RE9IZFBWR2QxWXpOa2JRPT0=','0','0','http://s.61baobao.com/common/flash/2011b/08/098.swf','http://www.61baobao.com/common/flash/2011b/08/dpic/098.jpg','http://www.61baobao.com/common/flash/2011b/08/pic/098.jpg','0','三个月以上','0','','0','','0','0','0');");
