E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_game` values('2508','18','0','','','','1','admin','','1','0','1343229746','0','0','0','0','','','2508','0','0','0','0','0','0','香港-早晨2','1343229746','/spic/20120725/2924.jpg','0','1','1343229746','0','3','1','0','','0','','/d/file/swf/078.swf','667','479','老师昨天说：“一天之计在于成，一生之计在于勤，你知道什么意思吗”。那就是说要善用每一天，那就每天早上把事情计划好，如果想一生过的好，那就要勤奋学习，加倍用功。懂吗“','1','','0','','1','/dpic/20120725/2925.jpg','11008','VERKT2RtSlhNWFppYVRsdFlrZEdlbUZET0hsTlJFVjRXV2s0ZDA5RE9IZE9lbWQxWXpOa2JRPT0=','0','0','http://s.61baobao.com/common/flash/2011b/08/078.swf','http://www.61baobao.com/common/flash/2011b/08/dpic/078.jpg','http://www.61baobao.com/common/flash/2011b/08/pic/078.jpg','0','三个月以上','0','','0','','0','0','0');");
